creator: RPATL Church
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to RPATL, we seek to bring a piece of our home to you at any place and any time.

Stay connected by:
-Listening to Recent Sermons
-Connect to our Live Video Streaming
-Engage with RPATL Team through our app
-Connect directly with our Pastors Jose & Monica Gutierrez
-Give your offerings and Tithings through a secure and easy way
-Enhance your experience as an RPATL guest or member

Bienvenidos a RPATL, deseamos darte una parte de nuestro hogar a cualquier hora en cualquier lugar.

Mantente conectado con:
-Escuchar recientes predicación
-Conéctese a nuestra transmisión en vivo
-Integrarse con el equipo RPATL a través de nuestra aplicación
-Conectarse directamente con nuestros pastores Jose y Monica Gutierrez
-Dar tus ofrendas y diezmos de forma segura y sencilla
-Mejorar tu experiencia como invitado o miembro de RPATL
descriptionShort: Connect and stay tuned with RPATL. Conéctese y manténgase informado con RPATL.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- New Media Search Experience with support for Speakers, Topics, and Scripture tags
- New Related media section on Media Items shows other media tagged with the same Topics
- Enhanced user profile with additional field and a direct integration to our CMS for Messaging Customers
- Misc. bug fixes and improvements.
